Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.92,0:58:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,literatura espiritual, escuchar a oradores y visitar\Nlugares sagrados.   He
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.96,0:58:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sí.\NY sin embargo, una cosa permanecerá
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.20,0:58:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,igual.  You say, "How can that be? How can\Nthat be?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.92,0:58:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How come it doesn't sink in? How come I\Ndon't get it? How come I'm not
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.07,0:58:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,transformed by the wonderful truths I've\Nheard?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.76,0:58:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\Nresearch today. There seems to be a
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.24,0:58:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,great block, isn't there? Uh we're\Nwilling to be loving towards all people.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.68,0:58:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We noticed that in Walmart that happens.\NEverybody was friendly. If I came down
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.79,0:58:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the aisle yesterday, I was coming down\Nthe aisle. I had a bunch of blank
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.68,0:58:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,videotape things and I'm going down and\Nthis lady looks sweetly at me and she
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.35,0:59:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,says, "Oh, pardon me." She pulled out\Nall the way. How come everybody's so
