Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.28,0:59:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So it must be certain context allows the\Ntruth to sink through.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.92,0:59:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it is why it doesn't\Nsink in. Okay. Why it doesn't sink in
