Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.20,0:59:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,other words, to allow even one truth to\Nshoot through
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.16,0:59:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is the beginning of the end for the ego.\NThat's correct.
