Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.07,1:00:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,just saw is true. Okay. Okay. All right.\NThat's what we're building up to the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.59,1:00:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,lectures. Anyway,\Nuh what we said was um you know what
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.44,1:00:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we're we're approaching it from the side\Nof the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.04,1:00:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,because when we get to lecture whatever\Nit is about the heart,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.48,1:00:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want the heart impeded by the\Nstructures of the ego. So first  we're
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.35,1:00:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,disassembling the ego. You see the ego\Nbecomes weaker just by recognizing it
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.55,1:01:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,for what it is.\NIt already loses its divine authority.
